text: Habichtstraße is an elevated rapid transit station located in the Hamburg district of Barmbek-Nord, Germany. The station was opened in 1930 and is served by Hamburg U-Bahn line U3. == Service == === Trains === Habichtstraße is served by Hamburg U-Bahn line U3; departures are every 10 minutes. The travel time to Hamburg Hauptbahnhof takes about 15 minutes. ==Gallery== File:U-Bahnhof Habichtstraße Außenansicht 2.nnw.jpg|The station's exterior File:U-Bahnhof Habichtstraße Eingangsbereich.nnw.jpg|The station's interior == See also == * List of Hamburg U-Bahn stations ==References== == External links == * Line and route network plans at hvv.de Category:Hamburg U-Bahn stations in Hamburg Category:Buildings and structures in Hamburg-Nord Hamburg Habichtstr Hamburg Habichtstr
